item.title: Add Our Calendar
item.description: To add the UMFC calendar to Google Calendar: Visit Google Calendar. Click on the arrow next to “Other Calendars.” Select “Add a friend’s calendar.” Paste in c_bb23ea3e1dc4d5534b53566ba5955e9bf051104f80de5bc1cb14a5595e6bbbf1@group.calendar.google.com Click “Add.”

item.title: Schedule
item.description: This calendar is regularly updated with practice times, competitions, and other events. Add it to your calendar to stay updated.
